return {
	["If what you're saying is true - and I have no reason to doubt the words of my faithful |PLAYERNAME| - go to {Oldrak}. He will surely know how to help you."] = "Jezeli to prawda co mowisz - a nie mam podstaw by watpic w slowa moich wiernych, |PLAYERNAME| - udaj sie do {Oldrak}. On na pewno bedzie wiedzial jak ci pomoc.",
	["Oldrak has currently gone to the steppes. He is teaching the villagers there."] = "Oldrak obecnie udal sie na stepy. Naucza tam mieszkancow wioski.",
	["I will be the harbinger of bad news. The Crypt King has managed to regain a portion of power by consuming the essence of a defeated angel. The Crypt King may attempt to regain strength in the Down's Labyrinth. To prevent this, you will need the assistance of Gandalf."] = "Bede zwiastunem zlych wiesci. Krol krypty zdolal odzyskac czesc mocy poprzez pochloniecie esencji pokonanego aniola. Krol krypty moze probowac odzyskac sily w labiryncie downa. Aby temu zapobiec, bedziesz potrzebowac pomocy Gandalfa.",
	["As for an ordinary person, it's a great effort and sacrifice for someone you didn't even know. Know that your deeds have been noticed. From now on, we will patrol the land much more closely to find lost souls. Please, take this magical flare. Use the flare at the entrance to the Ghasstly Princess' cave. We will take care of delivering it to us. Meanwhile, unfortunately, I will have to close the heavenly road for you. When your time comes, it will be reopened. I will be {seeing}, adventurer."] = "Jak na zwyklego czlowieka, to wielki wysilek i poswiecenie, dla kogos kogo nawet nie znales. Wiedz ze twoje uczynki zostaly zauwazone. Od teraz bedziemy o wiele dokladniej patrolowac ziemie w celu odnalezienia zagubionych dusz. Prosze, wez te magiczna flare. Uzyj flary na wejsciu do jaskini ducha dupy. My sie zajmiemy dostarczeniem jej do nas. Tymczasem, niestety, bede musial zamknac dla ciebie te podniebna droge. Gdy nadejdzie twoj czas, zostanie ona otwarta z powrotem. {Zegnaj}, poszukiwaczu przygod.",
	["Hello, traveler. I am the Ghasstly Princess. Do you want to hear my {story}?"] = "Witaj podrozniku. Jestem duchem dupy. Czy chcesz uslyszec moja {historie}?",
	["Once upon a time, I was a beautiful princess. One day, I heard from my brother about approaching armies from the north. I had never heard that our kingdom lost a war, so I didn't {worry} about it."] = "Dawno dawno temu bylam sobie piekna krolewna. Pewnego dnia uslyszalam od mojego brata o zblizajacych sie wojskach z polnocy. Nigdy nie slyszalam zeby nasze krolestwo przegralo wojne, totez nie {przejelam} sie ta wiadomoscia.",
	["Yes, this time the day turned out differently for me. That day, while performing my daily routine, I suddenly heard the sound of many trumpets in the distance. I happened to be on one of the higher {towers} at the time."] = "Tak, tym razem dzien potoczyl sie dla mnie inaczej. Tego dnia, podczas wykonywania mojej codziennej rutyny, uslyszalam nagle dzwiek wielu trab w oddali. Akurat wtedy bylam na jednym z wyzszych pietr {wiezy}.",
	["When, worried about the sounds from outside, I approached the window, I saw a great barrage of spears and rocks hitting the very center of the tower from which I was looking out. In a moment, the entire floor began to collapse, and I started {falling} with it."] = "Gdy, zaniepokojona odglosami z zewnatrz, podeszlam do okna. Zobaczylam jak wielka salwa wloczni i glazow uderza w sam srodek wiezy, z ktorej wygladalam. Za chwile cala kondygnacja zaczela sie osuwac, a ja zaczelam {spadac} razem z nia.",
	["That's all I remember. Then I woke up here as a specter. I didn't know that the spirits whose bodies were once mistreated would be unable to move. I've been {waiting} here for a long time for someone to take me to the other side..."] = "To wszystko co pamietam. Nastepnie obudzilam sie tu, jako zjawa. Nie wiedzialam ze duchy, ktorych Ã³wczesne cialo zostalo poturbowane, beda niezdolne do ruchu. {Czekam} tu od dawien dawna, az ktos zabierze mnie na druga strone...",
	["But no one comes. Please, will you help me find peace and find someone who will send me to {heaven}?"] = "Ale nikt nie przychodzi. Prosze, czy pomozesz mi odnalezc spokoj, i znajdziesz kogos kto odesle mnie do {nieba}?",
	["Thank you, finally someone who wanted to listen to me."] = "Dziekuje, nareszcie ktos kto chcial mnie wysluchac.",
	["Magic carpets? Who could have knowledge of something like magical carpets? Although... maybe some desert dwellers might know something about it. I don't know what to do myself, maybe the nomads can help you, although they are not experts in magic."] = "Dywany? A ktoz moze miec wiedze o czyms takim, jak magiczne dywany. Chociaz. moze jacys mieszkancy pustyni moga cos o tym wiedziec. Sama nie wiem co robic, moze nomadzi Ci pomoga, chociaz na magii to oni sie nie znaja.",
	["It's wonderful that you managed to get so far. Please, here is my staff. Wilson Tag manifested itself in my dreams yesterday. He told me to go to... I don't remember who. Maybe it's silly, but you have to ask him about enchanting the carpet."] = "To wspaniale ze udalo sie Tobie az tyle. Prosze, oto moja rozdzka.\n Objawil mi sie wczoraj Wieslaw Wszywka. Mowil mi zebym udala sie do.. nie pamietam kogo. Moze to glupie, ale musisz zapytac go o zaczarowanie dywanu.",
	["You managed to get the carpet! Now try to go to the top of the mountain that the djinn mentioned. It's my only hope."] = "Udalo Ci sie zdobyc dywan! Sproboj teraz udac sie na szczyt gory, o ktorej mowil djinn. To moja jedyna nadzieja.",
	["Finally, I can end this charade. You, sucker. I'm not a princess, I'm the undead king of the crypt. An angel will arrive shortly, whom I can easily defeat and drain of all his power. You can't do {anything} about it."] = "Nareszcie, moge zakonczyc te szarady. Ty naiwniaczku. Nie jestem zadna ksiezniczka, jestem nieumarlym krolem krypty. Zaraz przybedzie tu aniol, ktorego bez problemu pokonam, i wysse z niego cala jego moc. Ty {nic} nie mozesz z tym zrobic.",
	["Yes, I can perform such a service. If you want me to help you, first you {help} me."] = "Tak, potrafie wykonac taka usluge. Jezeli chcesz, zebym Ci pomogl, to najpierw Ty mi {pomozesz}.",
	["Some time ago, I heard rumors about smuggling silicon wafers. High-ranked heroes and some god raiders were involved in the whole operation. Perhaps the best way to find the smuggling location and thus the warehouse for the goods is to penetrate their structure. To infiltrate their gang, you will have to live among them for weeks, months, years! When they trust you completely, you will be able to learn the storage location... Or you can hack their GPS, just like I did a moment ago. The interesting bit for me is in the underground, where heroes, god raiders, and their pets - bone beasts - have settled. If I believe the readings, it's the same cave where the black knight quest is, but I can't be a hundred percent sure."] = "Jakis czas temu slyszalem plotki o przemycie gofrow krzemowych. W cala akcje zamieszani byli wysoko postawieni herosi oraz jacys bog raiderzy. Byc moze najlepszym sposobem na znalezienie miejsca przemytu, a tym samym magazynu towaru bedzie przenikniecie ich struktur. Aby zinfiltrowac ich bande, bedziesz musial zyc wsrod nich tygodniami, miesiacami, latami! Gdy zaufaja Ci bez reszty, bedziesz mogl poznac miejsce przechowywania... Albo mozesz zhakowac ich GPS, tak jak ja przed chwila. Interesujace mnie zawiniatko jest w podziemiach, w ktorych zamieszkali hero, bog raiderzy, i ich zwierzatka - bone beasty. Jezeli wierzyc odczytom, to jest to ta sama jaskinia, gdzie jest black knight quest, ale nie moge byc tego w stu procentach pewny.",
	["Thanks for your help. Now I will handle your request. I will need 5 dead weights to enchant your carpet. I will place them all on the carpet, which should result in overflow, and the carpet's weight should become negative. Return when you have 5 pieces of dead weight."] = "Dzieki za pomoc. Teraz obsluze twoje zapytanie. Bede potrzebowac 5 dead weight aby zaczarowac twoj dywan. Uloze je wszystkie na dywanie, co powinno poskutkowac przepelnieniem, a waga dywanu powinna stac sie ujemna. Wroc jak zdobedziesz 5 sztuk dead weight.",
	["Did you lose a bag somewhere? Well..."] = "Zgubiles gdzies worek? No coz",
	["Please take this carpet. Remember that the flying function only works in specific places, namely on the peaks of the highest mountains. One of these peaks is surely in the Caribbean."] = "Prosze, oto twoj dywan. Pamietaj, ze funkcja latania dziala tylko w konkretnych miejscach, a dokladnie na szczytach gor najwyzszych gor. Jedna z takich z pewnoscia jest szczyt na karaibach.",
	["Return when you have exactly 5 dead weight."] = "Wroc, jak bedziesz miec dokladnie 5 dead weight.",
	["Magic carpets? What nonsense. If you want, I can {sew} the green carpet you're talking about, but don't expect any magical abilities."] = "Magiczne dywany? Co za bzdury. Jezeli chcesz to moge Ci {uszyc} ten zielony dywan o ktorym mowisz, ale nie licz na zadne magiczne zdolnosci.",
	["I will need the following: 5 spider silk, 1 red pillow, 1 {artist palette}."] = "Bede do tego potrzebowac: 5 spider silk, 1 red pillow, 1 {artist palette}",
	["GM Tomek stole the last palette from me. Now he's in Knurow."] = "Ostatnia muszle ukradl mi GM Tomek. Teraz przebywa w knurowie.",
	["Here is your carpet."] = "Prosze, oto twoj dywan.",
	["Return when you have all the items."] = "Wroc, jak juz bedziesz miec wszystkie przedmioty.",
	["I knew you were a thief, come out, Tomek! |PLAYERNAME|, I will need your help in the ritual to expel this thief. In return, I will help you recover the stolen item. And now, we begin: It's all your fault. The {Rat King} will decide your fate!"] = "Wiedzialem, ze jestes zlodziejem, wylaz, tomek! |PLAYERNAME|, bede potrzebowac pomocy w rytuale wypedzenia tego zlodzieja. W zamian pomoge w odzyskaniu ukradzionego przedmiotu. A teraz, zaczynamy: To wszystko twoja wina. O twoim losie zadecyduje {Krol Szczurow}!",
	["Rat King! Psst, now say: {away to the Ratlands}."] = "Krol Szczurow! psst, teraz powiedz: {won do szczurolandii}",
	["TO THE RATS! SWIRL OF STENCH! It was all {his fault}."] = "DO SZCZUROW! WIR SMIERDZIELU! To wszystko byla {jego wina}.",
	["And there he goes, sucked and swirled away. Here you go, the palette you were looking for."] = "I poplynal. Prosze bardzo, oto paleta, ktorej szukales.",
	["Assortment of paints. Can be used to paint any surface."] = "Paleta kolorow. Mozna nia malowac po kazdej powierzchni",
	["Box of sillicon wafers. Jannah' ma might be interested in it"] = "Pudlo z waflami krzemowymi. Jannah'ma moze byc nim zainteresowany",
	["Flare from Aunor. Use it before Ghasstly Princess's cave entrance"] = "Flara od Aunora. Uzyj jej przed jaskinia ducha dupy",
	["Aurnor has prevented you from using this path."] = "Aunor zamknal dla ciebie te sciezke.",
	["A magical force brought you back to the solid ground."] = "Magiczna sila sciagnela cie z powrotem na ziemie.",
	["You have to be standing just before Ghasstly Princess's cave in order to use this flare."] = "Musisz stac przed jaskinia ducha dupy, aby moc uzyc flary.",
	["Flying rats? Carpets? I see you that you have imbibed a FoV potion. You can ask about those things in the vilage of the most generous {creatures}."] = "Latajace szczury? Dywany? Rozumie sie ze pan juz po napoju na FoV. Takimi rzeczami palaja sie tylko najbardziej szczodre {istoty}.",
	["Im talking about the {djinn} of course. They will get you drunk for free, and the best thing is they dont charge for it."] = "Mowie oczywiscie o {Djinnach}. To oni upijaja czlowieka za darmo, i nawet nie trzeba placic.",
	["You will find them in Hurghada desert. Can't say i recall anything more because last time i was here they had to tow me back to my home, if you know what i mean.."] = "Znajdziesz ich na Hurghadzie. Dokladniej nie pamietam, bo ostatnio mnie stamtad odholowywali, jezeli wiesz o czym mowie.",
}
